/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/library/factual/exact-rewrite-architecture-screening/same-currency-comparisons-only-count-on-the-same-full-lei-object-protocol-and-charged-debt.md:10:and after the same pressure-recovery and admissibility debt has been charged.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:5:This branch is only live after one stable notion of a near-closed Tao circuit has been fixed. Given that frozen object, the question is whether exact Navier-Stokes forces a uniformly nontrivial off-circuit transfer on an explicit packet class, or whether an adversarial family can drive that transfer to zero while preserving the intended Tao-role logic over a stated activation window.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:17:This chain no longer treats leakage as a freely chosen ratio, no longer assumes minimal finite packets are decisive, and no longer jumps from closure bookkeeping to theorem rhetoric. It is a downstream quantitative test on one frozen near-closure definition, one packet class, one observable, and one declared time window.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:25:Action: adopt one near-closure definition that is already stable under packetization, normalization, conjugate completion, and basis bookkeeping. If no such object has been supplied by the definition-audit branch, stop immediately.
