+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Freeze tolerances
+
+  ```text
+  lambda_tmpl = 1/3,
+  lambda_spec = 1/4.
+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Candidate passes on a family only if
+
+  ```text
+  Delta_tmpl <= 1/3
+  and
+  Delta_spec <= 1/4.
+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Diagnostic vector to retain:
+
