+- `[INFERRED]` **A_live.**
+  A family may be evaluated positively only if
+  `int_I D_on(t) dt > 0`.
+  This blocks vacuous wins from static cancellation packets such as exact
+  Beltrami alignment.
+- `[VERIFIED]` **A_sheet.**
+  The family must use the frozen packet semantics, mandatory conjugate
