+    := |Q_clk(t)| + |Q_seed(t)| + |Q_amp(t)|
+       + |Q_rot^D(t)| + |Q_rot^A(t)| + |Q_next(t)|
+
+  D_off(t)
+    := D_mirror(t) + D_companion(t) + D_feedback(t) + D_cross(t).
+  ```
